        <p data-role="text">There are ben&#xAD;e&#xAD;fits to ar&#xAD;ti&#xAD;fi&#xAD;cial in&#xAD;tel&#xAD;li&#xAD;gence tech&#xAD;nolo&#xAD;gies like this one which can pre&#xAD;dict the sever&#xAD;ity of pneu&#xAD;mo&#xAD;nia in a pa&#xAD;tient based on an X-ray im&#xAD;age. But AI can also run amok with un&#xAD;in&#xAD;tended out&#xAD;comes.</p>
    </div>

